install vmware workstation player 17. double click and install it and click on next button
accept the license and click on next
select add vmware workstation console tools into system path and click on next
select both check box in user experience setting and click on next
vmware workstation 17 is ready to install
click on open a virtual machine
now give name to your virtual machine and redirect folder where your .iso file is located
click on create a new virtual machine
